Details: Red & White Multimedia Education is an ISO 9001:2008 certified firm that offers certified courses. Red & White Multimedia Education established in 2008. Red & White Multimedia Education provides development services in various technologies like ASP.Net, VB.Net, C#.Net, MS SQL Server, PHP, HTML5, XHTML, CSS3, Ajax, JQuery & Open Source framework like WordPress , CodeIgniter, etc. and Mobile application design for I-Phone, Android, Windows & BlackBerry and also Mobile application development for Android. Red & White Multimedia Education also provides training in animation field like Video editing, 2D-3D Animation, etc.  Red & White Multimedia Education are a professional web and software development Institute as well as offshore development firm based in Surat, India. Our software development Institute in surat with focus on .Net, PHP, Java, Web Design, Video Editing , Animation ,CAD( Mech. / Civil ) training , 3Ds Max, etc. We provides Training and Software Development services. We offers Live Project training or Internship to the students of IT stream like B.E. IT, BE Comp, MCA, BCA, Diploma students, B.Sc.IT, M.Sc.IT. Our strong roots in software industry ensure that you will work on Live Projects of software development, web development and integration.  We are inviting Final year student of IT stream for project training. The candidate will have most of the chances that they will be recruited as our employee after completion of their training period. Student will also work on live project of our offshore clients.  Red & White Multimedia Education provide Live Project PHP, ASP.NET, JAVA, for Fresher and IT enthusiast at Surat. Are you near to complete your BE (Computer Application, Electronics)/ B.Tech (Computer Application)/MCA (Master of Computer Application) / B.Sc.IT Course? and yet have not done your project in the lack of efficiency?... Come to Red & White Multimedia Education and complete your project work with guidelines of our professionals and experts in the industrial environment. We provides training for IT students such as MCA / BCA / Engineering (Degree/Diploma) / M.Sc. ?? B.Sc. IT in ASP.Net and PHP, Java. We provide 6th semester Project Training by Industrial experts. This training provides industrial exposure to the candidates & helps the candidate to find a suitable job in IT industries. Here, our experienced and highly skilled professionals will guide you in all ways, whenever and wherever you require. Under our proficient guidance, you will not only complete your project successfully, but also guide your way to be successful software professional in the future.   You will be working on International Live Projects and will be able to complete in desired timeline with help of our experienced team members. Project will be completed under experts supervision of project managers in the Institute. Students of IT /Comp. /Mech. /Civil Colleges from Gujarat (Surat, Valsad, Bardoli, Navsari, etc..) can join us

Business Excellence Institute Private Limited (BEI) is a Global Management Consulting, Training, Assessment and Certification Services Provider for organizations worldwide with a mission to promote excellence in the organizations for the benefit of society. BEI provides services to corporate as well as individuals for excellence all over the world includes research, consulting, training, assessment and certification.The vision of our institute is to empower one million business leaders and organizations truly succeed in their business ventures to create wealth for the society and support professionals all through their careerBEI Trainers: All our Quality trainers are MBB from ISI, ASQ or MNC companies having more than 12 years experience and all our Project Management trainers are certified PMP or PGMP having more than 10 years experienced in MNC companies.BEI provides independent international personnel certification as per ISO 17024 standards which is valid worldwide. Choose your certification and build a successful career
BEI provides training in the areas of Six Sigma, Project Management (PMP0, PISO, HR, Finance, Leadership, Marketing, & Business Communication. Contact us for further details @ 7795342711 & 8123219356.

Details: Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics (MAAC) is India's foremost institute for excellence in the field of animation and computer graphics. We take great pride in our intuitive philosophy of evolving over strong conceptual knowledge, which enables us to focus, more on talents conceptual base before evolving on to its practical sciences. The 3D animation and visual effects industry in India has become one of the hottest industries with the Govt. of India lending full support by way of recognising the entertainment industry and with NASSCOM putting positive figures and optimism on its growth. MAAC offers the most advanced environment to its students in terms of infrastructure, academic curriculum, and seasoned professionals as faculties for cultivating creative skills and knowledge in animation and computer graphics. The institute stands out from the rest by providing the best exposure to the international animation industry. Hence, it allows the students to get exposed to the latest development and technology all over the world. MAAC is also credited with being the largest Auto Desk Authorized Training Centers (ATC), the global leaders in animation software. On an average, MAAC trains 11,000 students every year, providing them with a true-to-studio study environment, state-of-the-art infrastructure facility, an extensive curriculum, and the benefit of a highly experienced faculty.Placements by MAAC & its contribution to the Indian animation industry: The animation industry offers career opportunities in a range of activities - from technology-based jobs such as scanning, compositing, digital ink and paint, and game designing to creative guys like visual-effects supervisors, 3D modellers, and character animators.MAAC offers a highly integrated curriculum to its students from the initial sketching phase to the final on-screen animation phase, helping in building a talent pool of studio-ready students, who can confidently fill up the growing gap between demand and supply of quality animators. Moreover, strongly networked placement division helps its students secure credible placements at various animation studios and allied sectors. Valued production houses like Rhythm & Hues, Crest Communication, Pixion, Prana, Tata Elxsi, U TV, Ani-rights, Prime Focus, Data Quest, etc., conduct campus interviews at MAAC centres and absorb students even before they have completed the course. These production houses are majority catering to international projects from different parts of the globe outsourced to Indian animation market.New courses introduced at MAAC: To move on with the international animation market, MAAC has always been in the process of upgrading its course structure to service future demand and based on the feedback from production experts, we have optimised and introduced new technologies and applications in our new programAD3D. It is designed keeping in mind the latest trends in production techniques and technologies used in top studios and production houses.As you are looking for a short-term course/specialized animation course/career course, we suggest you visit our website: www.maacindia.com. Details: Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics (MAAC) is India's foremost institute for excellence in the field of animation and computer graphics. We take great pride in our intuitive philosophy of evolving over strong conceptual knowledge, which enables us to focus, more on talents conceptual base before evolving on to its practical sciences. The 3D animation and visual effects industry in India has become one of the hottest industries with the Govt. of India lending full support by way of recognising the entertainment industry and with NASSCOM putting positive figures and optimism on its growth. MAAC offers the most advanced environment to its students in terms of infrastructure, academic curriculum, and seasoned professionals as faculties for cultivating creative skills and knowledge in animation and computer graphics. The institute stands out from the rest by providing the best exposure to the international animation industry. Hence, it allows the students to get exposed to the latest development and technology all over the world. MAAC is also credited with being the largest Auto Desk Authorized Training Centers (ATC), the global leaders in animation software. On an average, MAAC trains 11,000 students every year, providing them with a true-to-studio study environment, state-of-the-art infrastructure facility, an extensive curriculum, and the benefit of a highly experienced faculty.Placements by MAAC & its contribution to the Indian animation industry: The animation industry offers career opportunities in a range of activities - from technology-based jobs such as scanning, compositing, digital ink and paint, and game designing to creative guys like visual-effects supervisors, 3D modellers, and character animators.MAAC offers a highly integrated curriculum to its students from the initial sketching phase to the final on-screen animation phase, helping in building a talent pool of studio-ready students, who can confidently fill up the growing gap between demand and supply of quality animators. Moreover, strongly networked placement division helps its students secure credible placements at various animation studios and allied sectors. Valued production houses like Rhythm & Hues, Crest Communication, Pixion, Prana, Tata Elxsi, U TV, Ani-rights, Prime Focus, Data Quest, etc., conduct campus interviews at MAAC centres and absorb students even before they have completed the course. These production houses are majority catering to international projects from different parts of the globe outsourced to Indian animation market.New courses introduced at MAAC: To move on with the international animation market, MAAC has always been in the process of upgrading its course structure to service future demand and based on the feedback from production experts, we have optimised and introduced new technologies and applications in our new programAD3D. It is designed keeping in mind the latest trends in production techniques and technologies used in top studios and production houses.As you are looking for a short-term course/specialized animation course/career course, we suggest you visit our website: www.maacindia.com.
